493
00:21:55,272 --> 00:21:57,525
He left me?!

494
00:21:59,068 --> 00:22:00,820
[SEIYA panting]

495
00:22:00,861 --> 00:22:03,864
[RISTA] Hey, speedy,
what's the big idea?!

496
00:22:03,906 --> 00:22:05,115
[giggles]

497
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:06,325
[MACHINA]
Running away without thinking

498
