Well, how fascinating!

501
00:22:14,708 --> 00:22:17,711
Yes. What a fascinating hero!

502
00:22:19,797 --> 00:22:21,382
Wait for me!

503
00:22:21,423 --> 00:22:26,929
You'd run away and
leave a goddess behind?!

